OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start.
OL,6,FSunny spells will turn hazy during the
OL,7,Fday with patchy light rain pushing
OL,8,Finto Kintyre and the west coast.
OL,9,FFeeling pleasant in any sunshine,
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain pushing
OL,13,Feastwards, mostly light and patchy,
OL,14,Fbut the odd heavier burst possible
OL,15,Fover the hills. Turning more showery
OL,16,Fovernight and milder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
