OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fbest of the brightness expected during
OL,7,Fthe morning. The showers could be
OL,8,Fheavy, perhaps the odd rumble of
OL,9,Fthunder. Moderate westerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and bright on Monday with early
OL,13,Fshowers dying out. Rain or showers on
OL,14,FTuesday and Wednesday, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
